stylometry: It is more difficult to solve integer programming modles because there are situations that have many  different types of solutions.  Having all of these solutions makes it very difficult to solve these problems with the formulas and solver we have used for other problems.  With dealing with 0-1 models we have to consider the exponent as the total possible of solutions.  For instance if the number was 2^10 power this problem or model has a total of 10 different solutions.  Alogrithms help take these different solutions and gives the one most appropriate for the information and model you are working with.
